Implats has concluded agreements to acquire a further 1,003,495 RBPlat Shares constituting approximately 0.35% of the RBPlat Shares in issue. Implats will hold RBPlat Shares comprising an aggregate of approximately 35.66% of the RBPlat Shares in issue. Implats confirms that these acquisitions have already been disclosed to the Takeover Regulation Panel as required under Chapter 5 of the Companies Regulations, 2011.